## Get QR-code for OTP

> Headers

```
Content-type: application/json
```

> Body example

```json
{
    "shop_id":        "...",
    "shop_secret":    "...",
    "identifier":     "..."
}
```

> Request example

```shell
curl --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
  --request POST \
  --data-binary "@data.json" \
  https://<%= config[:api_endpoint] %>/loyalty/qr/get
```

